00:47:30,760 --> 00:47:32,520
Have you started taking notes?

400
00:47:34,360 --> 00:47:37,760
MY NAMES IS AGAH BEYOGLU.
I THREW MY TV INTO THE STREET.

401
00:47:39,480 --> 00:47:41,720
- I'm taking notes, yes.
