you always wanted to do but you couldn't.

418
00:48:46,040 --> 00:48:47,720
There are many things I want to do.

419
00:48:47,800 --> 00:48:49,520
That's it, very good.

420
00:48:50,040 --> 00:48:53,400
Look, whatever it is,
however it is done...

421
00:48:54,280 --> 00:48:56,640
